{"tid":2116353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"禁足令？","createTime":"2020-07-20T06:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T06:20:12.000Z","uid":180156,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e796fd59f3ff821f45a1e90a77a2dfc4e8770bd","tid":2116353,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:03:38.000Z","msg":"你估我好想出街？<br />\n無屋企點返 返到屋企家嘈屋閉 <br />\n唔俾堂食已經要喺條街食飯 依加仲想行禁足令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府官員個個有糧出有靚屋企日撚日留喺屋企都得拉 實行乜撚嘢措施都唔影響佢地生活 <br />\n<br />\n喺大教授政府眼中香港無窮人架 全撚部人都住大屋 有穩定收入 全家家庭和諧 所以大家都可以留喺屋企抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471e35aa2935473760c9f94c71e3d79627c2b504","tid":2116353,"uid":10503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b8rYsQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb8rYsQY.jpg&h=9ccbbe97&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ZwNmaY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ZwNmaY.png&h=2469abbd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wi2s5CE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWi2s5CE.jpg&h=0974236d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f28fdd2de2888e69b3344e3b96e6e5753ff9420","tid":2116353,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:05:42.000Z","msg":"如果要禁足,咁我寧願喺酒店禁喇."},{"pid":"53752e0b1322270cfaa53e06d283742b00777847","tid":2116353,"uid":392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C26hJqd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC26hJqd.png&h=593c3caf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1e58f925947cfbe046184c6bee1a166f2b6a58b","tid":2116353,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06